<title>
Uklanjanje i ugradnja krovne ploče
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Donja slika prikazuje uvjete za uklanjanje sljedećih dijelova.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Prednji blatobran 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A9A06005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0181.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "55.869mm" ver = "02" gw = "227" gh = "142"/>
</figure>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A9B06025001">
<title>
Opće napomene
</title>
<ptxt>
Konzole krovnog nosača će se ponovno koristiti.
</ptxt>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A9B06025002">
<title>
Uklanjanje
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Izbušite zavarene točke i uklonite 4 konzole krovnog nosača i krovnu ploču.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A9B0024.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "215.042mm" ver = "01" gw = "467" gh = "593"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.438in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.472in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "4.537in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[A]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Model bez krovnog prozora
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MANOTE" width = "5.132mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
 :
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Kad zagrijavate oko nanesenog dijela brtvila kako biste odvojili brtvilo karoserije, pobrinite se da temperatura navedenog dijela ne dostigne 170 &#176;C (338 &#176;F).
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[B]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Model s krovnim prozorom
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A9B06025003">
<title>
Ugradnja
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Prije zavarivanja, provjerite položaj za ugradnju i uvjete za pravilnu ugradnju dijela (dijelova). 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A9B04005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
 / 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A9B04008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Provedite privremeno zavarivanje na središnjem nosaču krovne ploče br. 2 (samo model bez krovnog prozora),središnjem nosaču krovne ploče br. 3 i središnjem nosaču krovne ploče br. 4.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Nanesite brtvilo za karoseriju na prednju unutarnju krovnu vodilicu, središnji nosač krovne ploče br. 2 (samo model bez krovnog prozora), središnji nosač krovne ploče br. 1 (samo model bez krovnog prozora), pojačanje kliznog krova (samo model s krovnim prozorom), središnji nosač krovne ploče br. 3, središnji nosač krovne ploče br. 4 i stražnji unutarnji nosač krova.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0179.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "204.967mm" ver = "04" gw = "426" gh = "564"/>
